e9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh\">T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien.html\/#To_chuc_Hoi_nghi_tri_an_khach_hang\" title=\"T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb tri \u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng\">T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb tri \u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien.html\/#To_chuc_su_kien_Tiec_cuoi_nam_-_Gala_Dinner\" title=\" T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Ti\u1ec7c cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m &#8211; Gala Dinner\"> T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Ti\u1ec7c cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m &#8211; Gala Dinner<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien.html\/#Dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_o_dau\" title=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien.html\/#Quy_trinh_to_chuc_su_kien_cua_A_Chau_Media\" title=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\">Quy tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\r\n<p><em>V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a <strong>s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/strong> c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u01a1n xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, gia t\u0103ng nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch v\u00e0 x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kinh doanh. C\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4915\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/am-thanh-su-kien-2.jpg\" alt=\"d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n\" width=\"851\" height=\"638\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/am-thanh-su-kien-2.jpg 960w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/am-thanh-su-kien-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/am-thanh-su-kien-2-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Uy_tin_chuyen_nghiep\"><\/span><strong>Uy t\u00edn chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Multimedia<\/strong> lu\u00f4n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang h\u1eb9n, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Theo d\u00f5i s\u00e1t xao trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n. T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean d\u00e1m s\u00e1t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Y_tuong_sang_tao\"><\/span><strong>\u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, set up s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/kich-ban-to-chuc-su-kien.html\/\">k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/a> \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, m\u1edbi l\u1ea1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. V\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng; \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea3n ch\u00e0o m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, hay nh\u1ea5t. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean m\u00e3n.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Toi_uu_chi_phi_thoi_gian\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed1i \u01b0u chi ph\u00ed, th\u1eddi gian<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n mang l\u1ea1i cho qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u01b0u, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c di\u1ec5n ra nhanh nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4916\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/IDOL-ra-mat-su-kien-sony.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n\" width=\"851\" height=\"462\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_chuc_su_kien_tai_A_Chau_Multimedia\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Multimedia<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n<p><strong>\r\n\r\n<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_chuc_Hoi_nghi_hoi_thao\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o, h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, t\u1ecda \u0111\u00e0m l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 doanh nghi\u1ec7p k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u kh\u1eaft khe ngay t\u1eeb kh\u00e2u ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00e1ch b\u00e0y tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng gian. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, l\u1ec5 t\u00e2n.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_chuc_su_kien_Ky_niem_thanh_lap_cong_ty\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n K\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ty<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u m\u1ed1c quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_chuc_su_kien_Khai_truong_khanh_thanh\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>L\u1ec5 khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 doanh nghi\u1ec7p gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m kinh doanh, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_chuc_Hoi_nghi_tri_an_khach_hang\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb tri \u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb tri \u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed7i doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u1eafm b\u1eaft nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft c\u00e1c m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_chuc_su_kien_Tiec_cuoi_nam_-_Gala_Dinner\"><\/span><br \/><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Ti\u1ec7c cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m &#8211; Gala Dinner<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Ti\u1ec7c t\u1ea5t ni\u00ean, ti\u1ec7c cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m Gala Dinner l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong c\u00f4ng ty t\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 giao l\u01b0u t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_to_chuc_su_kien_o_dau\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00f4ng Ty Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Multimedia cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh th\u00e0nh. <strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/strong> t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh. T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng,&#8230;.<\/p>\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_to_chuc_su_kien_cua_A_Chau_Media\"><\/span><strong><span id=\"Quy_trinh_to_chuc_su_kien_ngoai_troi_cua_A_Chau_Media\" class=\"ez-toc-section\">Quy tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/span><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/li>\r\n<li>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n n\u1ed9i dung, l\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\r\n<li>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ebft m\u1ee5c bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n, ca s\u0129, MC, PG, l\u1ec5 t\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/li>\r\n<li>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb, ki\u1ec3m duy\u1ec7t v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra.<\/li>\r\n<li>Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n.<\/li>\r\n<li>K\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p><em>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n m\u00e0 \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media mu\u1ed1n cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, uy t\u00edn, h\u00e3y c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media v\u00e0 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u01a1n xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, gia t\u0103ng nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch v\u00e0 x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kinh doanh. C\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4918,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[89,88,91,90],"tags":[210,309],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 T\u1ed5 Ch\u1ee9c S\u1ef1 Ki\u1ec7n - C\u00f4ng Ty Qu\u1ea3ng C\u00e1o \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Multimedia<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, uy t\u00edn. C\u00f4ng ty Qu\u1ea3ng C\u00e1o \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Multimedia chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, tpHCM...\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien.html\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, uy t\u00edn. C\u00f4ng ty Qu\u1ea3ng C\u00e1o \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Multimedia chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, tpHCM...\" \/>\n<m